1
03:04:36,791 --> 03:04:38,125
What was that?

2
03:04:38,918 --> 03:04:41,295
- What happened?
- It fell. I saw it.

3
03:04:44,699 --> 03:04:45,949
It's dead.

4
03:04:50,096 --> 03:04:51,430
Smaug is dead.

5
03:04:52,306 --> 03:04:55,643
GLOIN:
By my beard, I think he's right.

6
03:04:56,060 --> 03:04:57,436
Look there!

7
03:04:57,939 --> 03:04:59,279
[RAVENS CAWING]

8
03:04:59,530 --> 03:05:03,242
The Ravens of Erebor
are returning to the Mountain.

9
03:05:04,410 --> 03:05:06,787
BALIN: Aye. Word will spread.

10
03:05:07,037 --> 03:05:10,958
Before long every soul
in Middle-earth will know...

11
03:05:11,208 --> 03:05:13,293
...the dragon is dead!

12
03:05:14,545 --> 03:05:16,545
[DWARVES LAUGHING]

